document.full_text: turkey said on thursday it had received a request from israel to help stop activists sailing to gaza on the first anniversary of an israeli raid on a turkish ship, but it said the flotilla plan was not ankara's concern.
document.title: turkey tells israel: gaza flotilla not up to us
